      <title>通货膨胀降温，阿根廷出人意料地将利率下调至 80%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-12/argentina-cuts-rates-to-80-in-surprise-move-as-inflation-cools</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿根廷央行出人意料地将基准利率从 100% 下调至 80%，原因是政策制定者预计月度通胀降温，而平行市场上比索兑美元继续走强。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-12/argentina-cuts-rates-to-80-in-surprise-move-as-inflation-cools</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 01:21:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
